1.12.0.name: drupal/fillpdf_token

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

1.12.0.description: Provides additional tokens for use in FillPDF mappings. You don't really need this module unless you want to use more Ubercart Ordered Product tokens than Ubercart provided when this was written. Useless if you don't enable the Ubercart Order (uc_order) module.
